### DentFlow Staff API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5199
### All endpoints require Authorization header (JWT Bearer token)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5199/api/v1
@authToken = Bearer REPLACE_WITH_VALID_JWT

### ✅ Happy path — Create staff member (201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff-members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@clinic.com",
  "staffType": "Dentist",
  "role": "Dentist",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Get staff member by ID (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff-members/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — List staff members (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff-members?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Update staff member (200)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/staff-members/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@clinic.com",
  "staffType": "Dentist",
  "role": "Dentist",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Delete staff member (204)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/staff-members/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ❌ Validation error — Create staff member with missing required fields (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff-members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

###

### 🔒 Unauthorized — No token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff-members

###

### 🔍 Not found — Get non-existent staff member (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff-members/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

